Anyway, here a thread... <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showMessage?topicID=107.topic">pub6.ezboard.com/fthemagi...=107.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
