<br>
Took 9 earth pets the first time (finished ~50% mana), 6 the second time (finished ~70% mana).<br>
<br>
Start out with a Bo3/DS'd earth pet, pull with Malosi.  Put pet on him and run to the other side of the island &amp; med.  Keep your pet targeted.  When pet dies, summon another *and damage shield him* (don't worry about bo3).  The dino will come running eventually (he's really kind of slow, you can outrun him with jboots).  Put the new pet on him when he gets to you, and repeat the whole process until he dies.  He starts to run at about 5 or 10% health.<br>
